name: SVGScriptElement
description: The SVGScriptElement interface corresponds to the SVG <script> element.

members.name: SVGScriptElement.type
members.description: A DOMString corresponding to the type attribute of the given <script> element. A DOMException is raised with the code NO_MODIFICATION_ALLOWED_ERR on an attempt to change the value of a read only attribut.

members.name: SVGScriptElement.crossOrigin
members.description: A DOMString corresponding to the crossorigin attribute of the given <script> element.
